# Prompt files

- **Location:** Keep prompts in `src/main/resources/prompts/` (e.g. `analyze-spec.txt`, `generate-code.txt`) so they are on the classpath and the generator can load them.
- **Placeholders:** Use clear placeholders (e.g. `{{SPEC_SUMMARY}}`, `{{TEST_CASES}}`) and document them in code or comments. Replace with actual values before sending to the LLM.
- **Instructions:** Be explicit about output format (e.g. "Return only the list of test cases, one per line") and constraints (REST Assured, TestNG, no soft assertions) so generated code matches project rules.
- **Versioning:** When changing prompts, consider backward compatibility of generated output; update tests or samples if the expected format changes.
